snippet.title: MOONCHILD- ACT 1 DEMO RELEASE DATE TRAILER!!!!!!!!
snippet.description:
Finally!! After so long, the end is in sight!!
As I may have mentioned before, this demo contains the first third of the entire game. And it'll be available for FREE in August!
When in August? That depends on how long polishing and filling in the last bits of content takes (and how many bugs, pop up, haha.)
I'll post a new devlog on steam with more details, but right now... I'm very tired. Look forward to it!

EDIT: Yeah, missed that month, sorry.
However, it WILL be coming out in the first week of November instead.

This trailer was edited by @TikTakDylan, please give him a subscribe if you liked it.

For more info about my upcoming projects, go to my Twitter and wishlist it on Steam!!
https://twitter.com/FrogInBoxStudio/
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2329110/Moonchild/
